    arr&lt;span class=&#34;token punctuation&#34;&gt;[&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;token number&#34;&gt;59&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;token punctuation&#34;&gt;]&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;token operator&#34;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;token number&#34;&gt;1&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;token punctuation&#34;&gt;;&lt;/span&gt;
